| **Resource Allocation** <br/> (Team Expertise, Timeline)                            | - Technical team size, skill set, availability.<br/>- Timeline for development vs. immediate availability.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  | - **In-House Talent:** If you already have a capable engineering & data science team, building might be feasible.<br/>- **Flexible Timeline:** If no urgent deployment is needed, you can allocate time for robust development and testing.                                                                                                                                               | - **Limited Internal Skills:** Offload core development to a vendor, quickly ramp up solution adoption.<br/>- **Faster Implementation:** Quick to go live if a solution is readily available.                                                                                                                                                                                              | - **Future Hiring or Partnerships:** If you plan to expand the team or partner with a specialized firm later, waiting might yield a stronger in-house build or better negotiation with vendors.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
